Crazy Dad
[[File:Crazydad2.jpg|thumb|right|-dad was here]]

[[File:Crazy_dad_hit_the_brown_trout.jpg|thumb|right]]
{{quote|Do your love son. Exactly what inside makes you shake and emit the desirable pounding throbbing name of a pulse...(do what moves you) see?|-dad was here}}

'''Crazy Dad''', also known as Jason Dionne is not only a delusional schizophrenic [[Red Sox Nation|Red Sox fan]], but a truly wise and loving father who rose to fame on [[4chan]]'s [[b/|/b/]] in May 2010. It all started when some kid started posting screenshots of his friend's dad on [[Facebook]]. Deemed "Crazy Dad" by the original poster, his inane and completely batshit insane responses to his children's facebook postings caught on quickly. Oh did we mention he is also an incestuous pedophile? See Exhibit A:

